Privacy Policy for Carizma Shop

Last Updated: May 24, 2025

Carizma Shop ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application ("App"). Please read this policy carefully.

Information We Collect

We collect the following types of information:

Personal Information





Account Creation/Sign-In: Email address, name, and password (encrypted).



User Details: Name, address, and phone number (if provided for orders).



Order History: Details of products ordered, including payment method (processed securely via third-party payment gateways).

Non-Personal Information





Cart and Favorites: Product preferences stored locally on your device using Hive.



Usage Data: Anonymized analytics (e.g., app interactions) to improve performance.

Locally Stored Data





Cart and favorites data is stored locally on your device using Hive and is not shared with us unless you place an order.

How We Use Your Information

We use your information to:





Create and manage your account.



Process and fulfill orders, including delivery and payment.



Provide personalized recommendations (e.g., best sellers).



Allow language switching (Arabic/English).



Display order history and user details.



Improve the App through anonymized analytics.

How We Share Your Information

We may share your information with:





Payment Processors: To process payments securely (e.g., Stripe, PayPal).



Delivery Partners: To fulfill orders (e.g., shipping address shared with couriers).



Legal Authorities: If required by law or to protect our rights.

We do not sell your personal information to third parties.

Data Security

We use industry-standard encryption (e.g., HTTPS for API calls) to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure. Locally stored data (cart, favorites) is protected by your device’s security features.

Your Rights

Under laws like GDPR (EU) and CCPA (California), you may:





Request access to your personal data.



Request correction or deletion of your data.



Opt out of data sharing (not applicable, as we don’t sell data).

To exercise these rights, contact us at privacy@carizma.shop.

Account Deletion

You can delete your account via the Account screen in the App. Upon deletion:





All personal data stored on our servers (e.g., user details, order history) will be removed.



Locally stored data (cart, favorites) will be cleared from your device.

Third-Party Services

The App uses third-party services, including:





Hive: For local storage of cart and favorites.



APIs: For fetching product and order data.



Payment Gateways: For secure payment processing.

These services have their own privacy policies, which we encourage you to review.

Children’s Privacy

The App is not intended for users under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children.

Changes to This Policy

We may update this policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. We will notify you via the App or email.

Contact Us

For questions or concerns about this policy, contact us at:





Email:



Website: https://carizmaelectric.com